    "description_long": "This is a large, modern pickup truck with a deep blue body and a spacious black cargo bed at the rear. The front features a prominent white grille and bumper, flanked by large side mirrors and angular headlights. The vehicle has four full-sized doors, chrome side steps, and oversized wheels with distinctive star-shaped rims. The windows are tinted black, and the roof has a row of small marker lights. The rear of the truck includes a tailgate, red taillights, and a visible towing hitch, making it suitable for both passenger and utility use in urban environments.",
